comments: [Observable in enhanced video] Hield (SAC) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.

Ferguson (OKC) legally contests Hield's (SAC) shot attempt.

RAR shows Adams (OKC) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Bagley III's (SAC) shot attempt.
RAR shows Grant (OKC) moves laterally into Bagley III's (SAC) body after his gather, affecting his driving shot attempt.
RAR shows Adams (OKC) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
RLB and RAR show Grant (OKC) reaches in and makes arm and body contact with Fox (SAC) that affects his driving shot attempt. The arm contact occurs prior to any contact with the ball.
Hield (SAC) legally contests Westbrook's (OKC) jump shot attempt.
Ferguson (OKC) places an arm to the front of Fox (SAC) and affects his SQBR.
Adams (OKC) is already in Barnes' (SAC) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Barnes (SAC) maintains legal guarding position as he defends George (OKC) on the perimeter.
[Observable in enhanced video] Adams (OKC) fails to fully clear and is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Bagley III (SAC) legally contests Grant's (OKC) jump shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Westbrook (OKC) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
LLB shows Adams (OKC) does not push Cauley-Stein (SAC) into Westbrook's (OKC) path at the end of the drive.

The crew communicated with the Replay Center official to determine if Cauley-Stein (SAC) was outside the restricted area as well as in legal guarding position prior to the contact from Westbrook (OKC).  After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor (offensive foul) was confirmed.
LAR and RAR show George (OKC) moves laterally into Hield's path (SAC) in an attempt to commit a take foul and the contact affects his SQBR.
Ferguson (OKC) attempts a take foul but Hield (SAC) stops short before the contact and is able to complete the pass.
Adams (OKC) commits a take foul on Barnes (SAC).
